{"tid":2166131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學者指美低估中共 侵台非吹牛","createTime":"2020-08-20T08:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T15:58:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":165,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"afd6c3c26db2db1f0fd3d9e1370e795081d3870f","tid":2166131,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:44:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/VOWC2LLNCVFP3FAWTEJR7OZK5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FVOWC2LLNCVFP3FAWTEJR7OZK5A%2F&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5dqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=6a0060e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200820%2FVOWC2LLNCVFP3FAWTEJR7OZK5A%2F&h=d1a81895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200820/VOWC2LLNCVFP3FAWTEJR7OZK5A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n學者指美低估中共 侵台非吹牛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QfCdgQ1x8w10HamhKGKQ5aySt8c=/1327x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R6FTCSU2A5BT7ODD2U2ATIOZGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQfCdgQ1x8w10HamhKGKQ5aySt8c%3D%2F1327x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR6FTCSU2A5BT7ODD2U2ATIOZGE.jpg&h=75b98d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴雅門<br />\n<br />\n中美兩國在台海一帶軍事動作頻繁，國際憂慮會有擦槍走火危險，「如果認為中共武統台灣的說法只是虛張聲勢那就大錯特錯，是極其危險的。」世界知名民主理論學者戴雅門（Larry Diamond）近日受訪時警告，美國大幅低估中共未來的危險性，又指中共入侵台灣絕不是吹牛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「虛張聲勢是錯覺」<br />\n<br />\n現任史丹福大學政治及社會學教授戴雅門，日前接受史丹福大學胡佛研究院的播客（podcast）採訪時說：「儘管希望中共是在虛張聲勢，但是我認為，說出中共虛張聲勢這句話本身是危險的，是錯覺。我們以為他們在香港問題上是這樣，結果不是。他們慢慢地蠶食，一步一步地扼殺了香港的自由。」<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，關於對付台灣不會有後果的說法，在中共內部獲得贊同，他相信中國已準備好攻打台灣，同時擔心未來20年的國際秩序：「美國外交政策和智庫極大低估了未來五到十年的危險。我們不僅應該加強和鞏固國際聯繫，而且還要特別注重亞太地區。」。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音"},{"pid":"f8cafd5ceb8cc0e706c61ddb53deb75598d64b9e","tid":2166131,"uid":79563,"like":63,"dislike":4,"score":59,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:45:19.000Z","msg":"打囉<br />\n<br />\n過到海峽咩？"},{"pid":"c26944e28861264aae9ec86335b6dd4eabb41509","tid":2166131,"uid":58209,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"有能力打同敢打係兩樣野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcf7d8b0eed22bffa07ed45b33f1c0a0295ddd6","tid":2166131,"uid":79563,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"c26944e28861264aae9ec86335b6dd4eabb41509","tid":2166131,"uid":58209,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"有能力打同敢打係兩樣野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:47:33.000Z","msg":"咪係<br />\n<br />\n100年前都對八國聯軍宣戰<br />\n<br />\n攻打北京使館區架<br />\n<br />\n要做實可以做架喎, WIN到先講啦"},{"pid":"9faa136849e4c6fa228e1f382830da84c530adeb","tid":2166131,"uid":62749,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"吹左幾十年, <br />\n就算最後真係打, 根本岸都登唔到<br />\n除非佢核平台灣, 血洗台灣當贏啦"},{"pid":"9fb5dd054a1e1b417c9d3093568489dc16e4e350","tid":2166131,"uid":19527,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:49:21.000Z","msg":"呢個未葡萄姐姐個老師？"},{"pid":"a0b911bf8d285bbd6566aea7f7824250ceaeab10","tid":2166131,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9faa136849e4c6fa228e1f382830da84c530adeb","tid":2166131,"uid":62749,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"吹左幾十年, <br />\n就算最後真係打, 根本岸都登唔到<br />\n除非佢核平台灣, 血洗台灣當贏啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:50:01.000Z","msg":"打囉<br />\n<br />\n用叮噹旋翼機過台海?"},{"pid":"6f0d2094e2e41f39152bcfec66f32246833d41e6","tid":2166131,"uid":330457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"驚你唔打咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f7e82eca12bf4120dfe9e2b523e172fc